    <string name="privacy_title">Your Data is Safe</string>
    <string name="privacy_desc">Nothing you write from the BanglaType keyboard ever goes outside your device. Words are kept only on your device in a special format for showing suggestions, which cannot be read directly. Even sensitive information like passwords or credit card info is never stored on your device. If someone expresses doubt about this on social media, please ask for proof. To stay completely safe, always install BanglaType keyboard from the Play Store. We are always committed to the security of your personal information. All data is offline.</string>
